Malaysia to Invest More Than 50 Billion Ringgit in Education

-- B y   E l f f i e   C h e w   a n d   C h o n g   P o o i   K o o n
-- 
2011-10-07T08:47:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/malaysia-to-invest-more-than-50-billion-ringgit-in-education.html
Malaysia pledged to invest more than
50 billion ringgit in education, Prime Minister Najib Razak said
in his budget speech in parliament in Kuala Lumpur today.  The government will also set up a 1 billion-ringgit fund to
build schools, he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
